---
const today = new Date();
---

<footer class="mt-10 mb-6 prose px-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
  <p>
    <a href="/blog" aria-label="Blog link">← Back</a>
    <button id="top-button" class="cursor-pointer float-right">
      <a>↑ Top</a>
    </button>
  </p>
  
  <hr />

  <p>
    <strong>max overflow</strong> is a blog about business, language, and
    computer science. Sometimes my thoughts overflow and end up here for
    safekeeping.
  </p>
  <p>
    For corrections (typos, factual inaccuracies), please file a 
    <a
      href="https://github.com/maxdemaio/max-astro/issues"
    >
      GitHub issue</a>.
  </p>

  <p>
    Website designed by Max DeMaio &copy; {today.getFullYear()}
  </p>
</footer>

<script>
  const topButton = document.querySelector('#top-button');
  if (!!topButton) {
    topButton.addEventListener('click', () => {
      window.scrollTo(0, 0);
    });
  }
</script>